- Create private key: openssl genrsa -des3 -out server.key 1024
- Create certificate request: openssl req -new -key server.key -out server.csr
- Create config file with following content to add `subjectKeyIdentifier`:

```
subjectKeyIdentifier=hash
```

- Create and self sign the certificate from certificate request: openssl x509 -req -days 365 -extfile ext.cnf -in server.csr -signkey server.key -out server.crt
- Verify details with: cat server.crt | openssl x509 -inform pem -noout -text
- Fetch certificate from any website: openssl s_client -showcerts -connect server.edu:443 </dev/null 2>/dev/null|openssl x509 -outform PEM >mycertfile.pem
